---

This product bundles `celiums-memory` v2.0 (the cognitive engine —
ethics pipeline, SHA-chained journal, PAD-circadian limbic, hybrid
retrieval) into the published artifact via tsup. The original
source is maintained at:

  https://github.com/terrizoaguimor/celiums-memory

celiums-memory is Apache-2.0 licensed. Every vendored file carries
the provenance header inserted by scripts/apply-vendor-headers.mjs:

    Copyright 2026 Celiums Solutions LLC
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
    Originally derived from celiums-memory v2.0
    (https://github.com/terrizoaguimor/celiums-memory, Apache 2.0)

---

The first install downloads two SHA-256-verified corpus artifacts
hosted outside this npm package, both Apache-2.0:

  - 10K-skill seed:        https://celiums-seed-public.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/seed/
  - ethics knowledge:      https://github.com/terrizoaguimor/celiums-memory/releases

Skipping either is supported via the corresponding CELIUMS_*_SKIP
environment variable (see README.md).
